{"tid":1874505,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"諷刺中國人播毒　足總勢罰迪利阿里停賽","createTime":"2020-02-11T08:45:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-11T11:48:17.000Z","uid":16659,"like":4,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"91d0e0e6fbcc61e66101687645cf354078e05c55","tid":1874505,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T08:45:52.000Z","msg":"新冠肺炎疫情嚴峻，世界各地都出現感染個案，雖然疫情已經威脅人類安危，但熱刺中場迪利阿里仍然當笑話咁玩，日前自拍影片放上社交網，片入面佢喺機場偷拍一名中國口音男子講嘢，話對方就係新冠肺炎病毒，又開玩笑話新冠肺炎病毒唔夠佢跑得快，所以「捉佢唔到」。<br />\n<br />\n影片公開後，迪利阿里被網民炮轟，涉嫌種族歧視、侵犯私隱以及作出不適當言論，呢位英格蘭球星事後亦刪片道歉，不過英國傳媒報道，英格蘭足總已經去信要求迪利阿里解釋事件，好可能會向佢作出處分。今季較早時間，曼城中場貝拿度施華曾經同隊友班捷文文迪喺社交網開玩笑，話文迪細個似一個朱古力品牌公仔，結果被判種族歧視停賽1場兼罰款5萬鎊，消息指迪利阿里將會面臨類似處罰，停賽勢在必行。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://football.on.cc/cnt/news/newe/index.html?articleId=bkn-20200211100637538-0211_00882_001&amp;whichpage=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffootball.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2Fnewe%2Findex.html%3FarticleId%3Dbkn-20200211100637538-0211_00882_001%26whichpage%3D1&d=e9hI6ag5UTzhCSVhase9yMZiPQ%2BZ2BAZCV%2B6nVsqWzo%3D&h=552444e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://football.on.cc/cnt/news/newe/index.html?articleId=bkn-20200211100637538-0211_00882_001&amp;whichpage=1</a>"},{"pid":"83201469edf1d56540f236928ca54bbe8fcd4b4e","tid":1874505,"uid":16659,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T08:46:32.000Z","msg":"中國人的確係播毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19e9bd8d97f1762e87ed827dfe173b412cf16eb8","tid":1874505,"uid":251052,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T08:46:50.000Z","msg":"日落帝國"},{"pid":"4c259ff128d2c7f47e14efe64d489a0f08552899","tid":1874505,"uid":44285,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T08:46:57.000Z","msg":"講事實又有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"725f8539e3029019245b4adf40c1fd232a490cb2","tid":1874505,"uid":61235,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"202